summary: Landscaped Proudspire is the second of a series of freestanding mods that add landscaping, subdued lighting and other aesthetics to the exteriors of Skyrims\' player homes. A simple esp file that adds no new textures or meshes. The pictures reflect the textures & meshes that I use... You will see your textures and meshes.
descriptionHtml:
Not a Beta version.. And will be Final unless I recieve reports of Massive Meltdowns :)
___________
Landscaped Proudspire is the second of a series of freestanding mods that add landscaping, subdued lighting and other aesthetics to the exteriors of Skyrims\' player homes. I\'m doing these as stand alone mods as these mods only effect the areas immediately around the player homes. I\'m not trying to Green up all of Skyrim, just make the players\' homes more appealing to the eye.
By not batching them all together, we gamers can chose and use the ones we like. 
___________
